txt.en: Grun Curldock can be found at Trader's Wharf.\n\nYou should talk to Grun Curldock.
'You have done as I asked? Very good. I thank you for assisting the League of the Axe, [placeholder].'

'The livelihood of the League depends upon trapping. It is important to keep the living things in the forest thriving, however. For that, we maintain a set number of traps in the Wildwood, no more.\n\n'I can see that we have many traps here at Trader's Wharf that could be set in the Wildwood. Would you set them for us? The League will be grateful.'
The League of the Axe uses traps to catch beasts for food and furs in the wilds of the Wildwood.
Good trap locations can be found in the Wildwood.\n\nYou should place the traps you have been given in the Wildwood.
